                    },
                    "body": "The Homebrew output shows a successful NumPy install\r\n{code:java}\r\n==> Installing dependencies for apache-arrow: numpy\r\n==> Installing apache-arrow dependency: numpy\r\n==> Pouring numpy-1.19.5.big_sur.bottle.tar.gz\r\n\ud83c\udf7a\u00a0 /usr/local/Cellar/numpy/1.19.5: 491 files, 16.3MB\r\n{code}\r\nbut then Arrow can't find NumPy.",
